|YKOAlignment is a player's outlook on life. In general, there are only
two aspects to alignment, good and evil. There are an infinite number 
of "shades of grey" between them however. Almost all monsters on 
Darkwind have their own alignment. Killing these monsters affects what 
your alignment is, shifting it in the opposite direction. For example, 
killing a holy paladin of Mitra (which is of good alignment) would shift 
your alignment towards the evil side of the spectrum.

